      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Leo visited the public library every Wednesday afternoon.",
              "audioStart": 0.1,
              "audioEnd": 3.138
            },
            {
              "text": "He liked to sit in the quiet corner near the history section.",
              "audioStart": 4,
              "audioEnd": 7.05
            },
            {
              "text": "One day, he found a small, white note inside an old book.",
              "audioStart": 7.912,
              "audioEnd": 11.438
            },
            {
              "text": "The note contained a beautiful poem about the silence of the library.",
              "audioStart": 12.3,
              "audioEnd": 15.537
            },
            {
              "text": "He felt a sudden interest in the person who had written it.",
              "audioStart": 16.4,
              "audioEnd": 19.05
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Leo decided that he would write a reply.",
              "audioStart": 19.913,
              "audioEnd": 21.975
            },
            {
              "text": "He placed his own poem inside the same book the next week.",
              "audioStart": 22.837,
              "audioEnd": 25.988
            },
            {
              "text": "He hoped that someone would find his answer.",
              "audioStart": 26.85,
              "audioEnd": 28.975
            },
            {
              "text": "Soon, he saw a new note waiting for him on the shelf.",
              "audioStart": 29.837,
              "audioEnd": 32.8
            },
            {
              "text": "This secret communication became the highlight of his week.",
              "audioStart": 33.663,
              "audioEnd": 36.638
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "He learned that the girl was named Mia.",
              "audioStart": 37.5,
              "audioEnd": 39.288
            },
            {
              "text": "She was a student who studied at the same library.",
              "audioStart": 40.15,
              "audioEnd": 42.625
            },
            {
              "text": "They exchanged many letters through the hidden pages of books.",
              "audioStart": 43.487,
              "audioEnd": 46.487
            },
            {
              "text": "If he had not found that first note, they would never have met.",
              "audioStart": 47.35,
              "audioEnd": 50.513
            },
            {
              "text": "Their relationship grew through the words they shared on paper.",
              "audioStart": 51.375,
              "audioEnd": 54.2
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Finally, Leo decided to leave a note with his name and phone number.",
              "audioStart": 55.062,
              "audioEnd": 58.513
            },
            {
              "text": "He wondered if Mia would be brave enough to call him.",
              "audioStart": 59.375,
              "audioEnd": 61.825
            },
            {
              "text": "The next day, his phone rang while he was at home.",
              "audioStart": 62.688,
              "audioEnd": 65.4
            },
            {
              "text": "He felt happy because he heard a soft voice on the other side.",
              "audioStart": 66.263,
              "audioEnd": 69.412
            },
            {
              "text": "It was Mia, and she wanted to meet him for coffee.",
              "audioStart": 70.275,
              "audioEnd": 73.025
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "They met at a local cafe outside the library.",
              "audioStart": 73.888,
              "audioEnd": 76.375
            },
            {
              "text": "They talked for hours about their favorite books and life.",
              "audioStart": 77.237,
              "audioEnd": 79.987
            },
            {
              "text": "It was a perfect afternoon for both of them.",
              "audioStart": 80.85,
              "audioEnd": 83
            },
            {
              "text": "They realized that they had much in common.",
              "audioStart": 83.862,
              "audioEnd": 85.975
            },
            {
              "text": "A new story had started for the young couple.",
              "audioStart": 86.838,
              "audioEnd": 89.062
            }
          ]
        }
